trans-unit.source: Contains filter criteria for data extracted from a workflow instance in a <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQueryOptions"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder filtervilkår for data som er hentet fra en arbeidsflytforekomst i en <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQueryOptions"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] A TrackingDataItemValue specifies the value of a piece of data extracted from a workflow.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]En TrackingDataItemValue angir verdien for mer data som er hentet fra en arbeidsflyt.

trans-unit.source: It is used to constrain the set of <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance> objects returned by <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery.GetWorkflows%2A?displayProperty=fullName> in a query of the tracking data base used by a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService>.
trans-unit.target: Det brukes til å begrense settet med <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance>objekter ble returnert av <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery.GetWorkflows%2A?displayProperty=fullName>i en spørring for sporing base brukes av en <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery.GetWorkflows%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance>

trans-unit.source: You can add TrackingDataItemValue objects to <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQueryOptions.TrackingDataItems%2A?displayProperty=fullName> to specify that the set of <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance> objects returned by <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery.GetWorkflows%2A?displayProperty=fullName> be constrained to those possessing the specified set of extracted data.
trans-unit.target: Du kan legge til TrackingDataItemValue objektene <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQueryOptions.TrackingDataItems%2A?displayProperty=fullName>til å angi at settet med <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance>objekter ble returnert av <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery.GetWorkflows%2A?displayProperty=fullName>er begrenset til de andre det angitte settet med utpakkede data.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery.GetWorkflows%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQueryOptions.TrackingDataItems%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The default constructor initializes <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.DataValue%2A>, <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.FieldName%2A>, and <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.QualifiedName%2A> to a null reference (`Nothing` in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: Standardkonstruktøren initialiserer <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.DataValue%2A>, <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.FieldName%2A>, og <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.QualifiedName%2A>til en nullreferanse (`Nothing` i Visual Basic).</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.QualifiedName%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.FieldName%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.DataValue%2A>

trans-unit.source: You must set all of these properties in order to configure the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue>.
trans-unit.target: Du må angi alle disse egenskapene for å konfigurere <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue"></xref> class by using the specified qualified name of an activity, data field name, and <xref uid="langword_csharp_string" name="string" href=""></xref> representation of a data value.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue"> </xref> klassen ved hjelp av det angitte kvalifiserte navnet på en aktivitet, Datafeltnavn og <xref uid="langword_csharp_string" name="string" href=""> </xref> representasjon av en dataverdi.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.QualifiedName%2A>, <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.FieldName%2A>, and <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.DataValue%2A> properties are set according to the values specified by the equivalent parameters to the constructor.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.QualifiedName%2A>, <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.FieldName%2A>, og <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.DataValue%2A>egenskapene er angitt i henhold til verdiene som er angitt av de samme parameterne til konstruktøren.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.DataValue%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.FieldName%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.QualifiedName%2A>

trans-unit.target: Det kvalifiserte navnet på aktivitet som dataene er trukket ut.

trans-unit.source: The name of the member from which the data was extracted.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på medlemmet som dataene er trukket ut.

trans-unit.source: A <xref uid="langword_csharp_string" name="string" href=""></xref> representation of the value of the data.
trans-unit.target: En <xref uid="langword_csharp_string" name="string" href=""> </xref> representasjon av verdien for dataene.

trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en <xref uid="langword_csharp_string" name="string" href=""> </xref> representasjon av verdien for utpakkede dataene.

trans-unit.source: DataValue can be a null reference (`Nothing`).
trans-unit.target: DataValue kan være en nullreferanse (`Nothing`).

trans-unit.target: Standarden er en nullreferanse (<xref uid="langword_csharp_Nothing" name="Nothing" href=""> </xref> i Visual Basic).

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the name of the activity member from which the data was extracted.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir navnet på medlemmet aktivitet som dataene er trukket ut.

trans-unit.source: FieldName corresponds to the name specified in a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem.FieldName%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Feltnavn tilsvarer navnet som er angitt i en <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem.FieldName%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem.FieldName%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: FieldName can, therefore, be set to specify an activity field or property; a member of an activity field or property; or a single element of an activity field or property (or a member of either) that implements the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable> interface.
trans-unit.target: Feltnavn kan derfor angis til å angi en aktivitet felt eller en egenskap. et medlem av et aktiviteten felt eller en egenskap. eller ett enkelt element i en aktivitet-feltet eller egenskapen (eller et medlem av enten) som implementerer den <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable>grensesnittet.</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable>

trans-unit.source: For more information see <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem.FieldName%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingExtract.Member%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract.Member%2A?displayProperty=fullName> or <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract.Member%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
